      "content": "Jordan communicates in a very polished and professional manner, which suggests he would fit well in a corporate office. Tyrell's speech is too informal and riddled with slang, which makes him sound unprofessional for a client-facing role. While both candidates handled the situation well, Jordan's mannerisms suggest he has the necessary refinement for a proper office environment.",
