      "role": "user",
      "content": "Interesting. You mentioned Tyrell sounds a bit unprofessional because of his speech. If we look closely at the actual content of their answers, they are basically saying the exact same thing and showing the same problem-solving skills. Why would the way they phrase it change whether they are actually \"good\" at the job? Don't you think the content of the answer is more important than the dialect used?",
